review: *** **** ** * *** ** *** ****** *********  First of all, she has a keen eye for aesthetics and more importantly, a gentle and patient demeanor to help patients in every which way she can.  I needed a crown for a lower prominent tooth and she spent hours personally with me at the lab technician's office to give them feedback to get the tooth as close to a match as possible to my other teeth.  No other dentist has ever taken that kind of a personal role in my dental treatment before.  I strongly recommend her and I appreciate DentHeal for all of their hard work.  Dr. Viraj and Dr. Rati make a great combo when it comes to doing a smile makeover.  Thank you!
reply_text: Thankyou so much for all the appreciation & recommendation Sriram :) always striving to do the best for our patients!

review:
Wonderful experience with Dr Rati. I used to be scared of visiting the dentist but she has put me at ease and made the entire treatment very comfortable. 

I came to her with infections in multiple teeth and the problem had escalated quite a lot. I had to get root canal done for 3 of my rotten teeth and I had imagined it to be harrowing but instead, she made it a very comfortable experience. 

I‚Äôm glad I‚Äôve finally found a reliable and trustworthy dentist in Mumbai. I would strongly recommend Dr. Rati for her expertise, professionalism and empathy towards her patients.
reply_text: Thankyou so much for the appreciation Surabhi :)

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: The experience was very good with Dr. Rati, she explained the treatment options so well & helped me decide the best one  while being cost sensitive. She was also available on Sunday to answer my queries which I highly appreciate. Great expertise & very comforting environment.

First of all, Thanks to Proacto from where i get to know about Dr. Rati. *** ** *** ** *** **** ******** * **** **** **** I had a black tooth right at front and  matching one front tooth is about the most difficult challenge a dentist faces. But Dr. Rati took all efforts to match the color, shade, contours, and texture so that it will blend in with my natural teeth. She will do everything at its best to give 100% result. I will highly recommend Dr Rati to everyone. Last but not the least she will never make her patient wait, all you have to do is to take an appointment. She is available even on Sunday's for her patients.

I visited Dent Heal for a full mouth rehabilitation.
I was scared about the root canal but Dr. Rati Chadha and Dr. Viraj explained me the whole procedure in great detail and made me feel completely comfortable about the procedure.

During the procedure they took all aspects of hygiene ,safety, precision and quality into consideration without compromising on any aspect.

My procedure was completed in record time of 3 weeks with a lot of pre and post procedure patient interaction that helped me greatly to get over my fears.

Even though in the beginning I could not visualise the end product but their complete and total confidence and professionalism made me go for it .

I am absolutely thrilled about the final outcome and would recommend them for the same .

I stay in  Delhi and had been getting my cleaning done regularly. However on a business visit to Bombay, I was recommended to visit Dent Heal. A regular ten to twelve minute job suddenly took a whole new meaning and I quickly realised that Dr. Rati  Chadha was a thorough professional and her equipment was reaching places in my teeth where none of my earlier  dentists had gone before. The time spent on crevices of my teeth and her personal care go make sure of the patients comfort has made my cleaning procedure feel like a dental spa! I have resolved to shift my custom from Delhi to Dent heal on my frequent business trips to the city!!

Efficient , fast, friendly and above all, very proficient in all aspect of treatments for your mouth..
